policy-options {
    policy-statement REDISTRIBUTE_APN_TO_BGP {
        term static_to_bgp {
            from {
                protocol static;
                route-filter 200.0.0.0/8 orlonger;
            }
            then accept;
        }
        term direct_to_bgp {
            from {
                protocol direct;
                route-filter 0.0.0.0/0 prefix-length-range /32-/32;
            }
            then accept;
        }
    }
    policy-statement REDISTRIBUTE_CN_TO_BGP {
        term direct_to_bgp {
            from {
                protocol direct;
                route-filter 0.0.0.0/0 prefix-length-range /32-/32;
            }
            then accept;
        }
    }
}

routing-instances {
    cn_1001_vpn {
        instance-type virtual-router;
        description "CN (RAN + Media) VEPC VPN - 103";
        interface ge-0/0/5.103;
        interface ge-0/0/6.103;
        interface lo0.103;
        routing-options {
            autonomous-system 65001;
            static {
                route 1.0.0.1/32 {
                    next-hop 41.1.3.1;
                    metric 254;
                    bfd-liveness-detection {
                        description "BFD to vrouter primary IP."
                        minimum-interval 1000;
                        minimum-receive-interval 1000;
                        transmit-interval {
                            minimum-interval 1000;
                        }
                        multiplier 3;
                        session-mode multihop;
                     }
                }
                route 1.0.0.2/32 {
                    next-hop 42.1.3.1;
                    metric 254;
                    bfd-liveness-detection {
                        description "BFD to vrouter primary IP."
                        minimum-interval 1000;
                        minimum-receive-interval 1000;
                        transmit-interval {
                            minimum-interval 1000;
                        }
                        multiplier 3;
                        session-mode multihop;
                     }
                }
            }
        }
        protocols {
            bgp {
                group cn_vsfo4ext1vlan103 {
                    type external;
                    export REDISTRIBUTE_CN_TO_BGP;
                    peer-as 64512;
                    description "CN (RAN + Media) VEPC VPN - 103 - peering session (ext 1)";
                    family inet {
                        unicast;
                    }
                    local-address 41.1.3.3;
                    neighbor 41.1.3.1;
                    neighbor 41.1.3.2;
                }
                group cn_vsfo4ext2vlan103 {
                    type external;
                    export REDISTRIBUTE_CN_TO_BGP;
                    peer-as 64512;
                    description "CN (RAN + Media) VEPC VPN - 103 - peering session (ext 2)";
                    family inet {
                        unicast;
                    }
                    local-address 42.1.3.3;
                    neighbor 42.1.3.1;
                    neighbor 42.1.3.2;
                }
            }
        }
    }
